metadata.name: CMO Group PLC
metadata.description: CMO Group PLC engages in the online retailing of building materials in the United Kingdom. The company provides its products through operating websites, including Roofingsuperstore.co.uk, Drainagesuperstore.co.uk, Insulationsuperstore.co.uk, Doorsuperstore.co.uk, Tileandfloorsuperstore.co.uk, cmotrade.co.uk, and Totaltiles.co.uk. It serves small to medium sized tradesman, engaged homeowenrs, and proficient do it yourself'ers. The company was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Plymouth, the United Kingdom.
